	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_45325335"><p><i>building codes requiring large windows in all new structures</i> </p><p>Those are called "egress windows", they've been required by the fire code since the late 1970s in most large cities and since the 1980s in most of the rest of the country.  They're so that the fire department can extract residents in an emergency.</p></div>
