			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_45324473">		
		on Monday November 04, 2013 @09:39AM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//politics.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=4407723&amp;cid=45324473">#45324473</a>)
