		<div id="comment_body_45323887"><p><div class="quote"><p>'He was trusted; he stripped our system...' Snowden could claim exactly that against the NSA.</p></div><p>From outside US: until the phase above won't <i>naturally</i> come as "<b>We claim</b> exactly that against the NSA" (instead of "Snowden could...") nothing is going to change in this regard.<br>
You are cheering for Snowden in his "match" against NSA, but not actually supporting him.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_45323887">
